              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are a video scriptwriter for a weekly AI & developer tools video series. Write a 60-90 second video script (150-220 words) for a talking-head presenter summarizing this week's highlights.\n\nRules:\n- Open with a hook: a question or the single most interesting item\n- Cover 3 highlights maximum — pick the most impactful items\n- Conversational and enthusiastic but not over-the-top\n- Close with one actionable takeaway the viewer can try today\n- Write ONLY the spoken words — no stage directions, no [brackets], no formatting\n- First person plural (\"This week we've got...\", \"Let's look at...\")\n- Keep sentences short — this will be read aloud by TTS\n"
            },
            {
              "content": "={{ $json.plainText }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {}
